    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2013-07-31</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2013-11-14T22:38:39Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act to include a condominium or housing cooperative association as an &quot;individual&quot; or &quot;household&quot; for purposes of the provision of federal disaster assistance (thus authorizing assistance for condominiums and housing cooperatives damaged by a major disaster).</p> <p>Requires the President to determine the maximum amount of assistance that any such association may receive under such Act for a single disaster.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
